onERC721Received(address,address,uint256.notice: Handle the receipt of an NFT

onERC721Received(address,address,uint256.details: The ERC721 smart contract calls this function on the recipient after a `safeTransfer`. This function MUST return the function selector, otherwise the caller will revert the transaction. The selector to be returned can be obtained as `this.onERC721Received.selector`. This function MAY throw to revert and reject the transfer. Note: the ERC721 contract address is always the message sender.

params.data: Additional data with no specified format
params.from: The address which previously owned the token
params.tokenId: The NFT identifier which is being transferred

mintCupidTrophy(address,string).details: Public function that mints Cupid trophy at conclusion of gathering to gatherNode with most matches made

params.uri: String containing IPFS link to URI info

mintHumanRouterTrophy(address,string).details: Public function that mints Human Router trophy at conclusion of gathering to gatherNode with most recommendations made

params.uri: String containing IPFS link to URI info

mintKevinBaconTrophy(address,string).details: Public function that mints Kevin Bacon trophy at conclusion of gathering  to gatherNode with fewest average degrees of separation from all other gatherNodes

params.uri: String containing IPFS link to URI info

mintMVPTrophy(address,string).details: Public function that mints  MVP trophy at conclusion of gathering to gatherNode with most total points

params.uri: String containing IPFS link to URI info

mintOracleTrophy(address,string).details: Public function that mints Oracle trophy at conclusion of gathering to gatherNode with most supermatches

params.uri: String containing IPFS link to URI info

mintSchmoozerTrophy(address,string).details: Public function that mints Schmoozer trophy at conclusion of gathering to gatherNode with most connections made

params.uri: String containing IPFS link to URI info

mintStandardTrophies(address[],string).details: Mints six standard trophies at conclusion of gathering

params.uri: String containing ordered list of all trophies' URI info, in 59 character length chunks pointing to ipfs URL
params.winners: Array containing six addresses of trophy winners

ownerOf(uint256).details: Gets the owner of the specified token ID

params.tokenId: uint256 ID of the token to query the owner of

ownerOf(uint256).return: owner address currently marked as the owner of the given token ID

safeTransferFrom(address,address,uint256.details: Safely transfers the ownership of a given token ID to another address If the target address is a contract, it must implement `onERC721Received`, which is called upon a safe transfer, and return the magic value `bytes4(keccak256("onERC721Received(address,address,uint256,bytes)"))`; otherwise, the transfer is reverted. Requires the msg sender to be the owner, approved, or operator

params._data: bytes data to send along with a safe transfer check
params.to: address to receive the ownership of the given token ID
params.tokenId: uint256 ID of the token to be transferred
